{{hatnote|In this Japanese name, the family name is Takeda.}}
[[Takeda Mika|<ruby>武田<rt>たけだ</rt></ruby>みか]] <small>({{langx|en|Takeda Mika}})</small> is an [[illustrator]] and a cartoonist.

